  body

    .container(role='main')
      a(href='/')
        img#logo(src='img/logo.png', alt='UCLA RADIO')

      #submissionStatus
        h1= status

      .row
        .col-md-6
          .mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.demo-card-wide 
            .mdl-card__title.staffing-points
              h2.mdl-card__title-text.black Staffing Points Form
            .mdl-card__supporting-text
              | Submit all your last minute points here.
            .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
              a.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect(target='_blank', href='http://bit.ly/1yWxyBP')
                | Go

        .col-md-6
          .mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.demo-card-wide 
            .mdl-card__title.total-points
              h2.mdl-card__title-text Staffing Points Totals
            .mdl-card__supporting-text
              | Double check that you still need 17 staffing points before tomorrow.
            .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
              a.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect(target='_blank', href='http://bit.ly/1H1M2Wc')
                | Go

      .row
        .col-md-6
          .mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.demo-card-wide 
            .mdl-card__title.in-station
              h2.mdl-card__title-text In-Studio Request Form
            .mdl-card__supporting-text
              | Fill this out if you want to have an artist come in to the station and perform.
            .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
              a.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect(target='_blank', href='http://bit.ly/1nZXeZh')
                | Go

        .col-md-6
          .mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.demo-card-wide 
            .mdl-card__title.concert-press
              h2.mdl-card__title-text Press Request Form
            .mdl-card__supporting-text
              | Want to go to a show for free? Fill this out. Remember you have to write a blog post about it!
            .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
              a.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect(target='_blank', href='http://bit.ly/1y1gPtt')
                | Go

      .row
        .col-md-6
          .mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.demo-card-wide 
            .mdl-card__title.substitution
              h2.mdl-card__title-text Sub Request Form
            .mdl-card__supporting-text
              | Feeling under the weather? Have a midterm tomorrow and haven't started studying? Fill this out to get a sub for your show. Do it at least 24 hours before the show.
            .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
              a.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect(target='_blank', href='http://bit.ly/Ru6JCE')
                | Go

        .col-md-6
          .mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.demo-card-wide 
            .mdl-card__title.spreadsheet
              h2.mdl-card__title-text Sub Request Spreadsheet
            .mdl-card__supporting-text
              | Check if someone already filled the sub request you wanted.
            .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
              a.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect(target='_blank', href='http://bit.ly/1qSA7i1')
                | Go

      .row
        .col-md-6
          .mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.demo-card-wide 
            .mdl-card__title.consent-and-release
              h2.mdl-card__title-text Consent and Release Form
            .mdl-card__supporting-text
              | Fill this out to be in one of our cool videos.
            .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
              a.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect(target='_blank', href='http://bit.ly/1DVZnhO')
                | Go

        .col-md-6
          .mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.demo-card-wide 
            .mdl-card__title.roster
              h2.mdl-card__title-text 2015-2016 Roster
            .mdl-card__supporting-text
              | Get on the Access List so you can get in when the dick who had his show before you closed the station door.
            .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
              a.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect(target='_blank', href='http://bit.ly/1vjBtpQ')
                | Go

      .row
        .col-md-6
          .mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.demo-card-wide 
            .mdl-card__title.calendar
              h2.mdl-card__title-text UCLA Radio Internal Calendar
            .mdl-card__supporting-text
              | See when our stuff is happening.
            .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
              a.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect(target='_blank', href='#')
                | COMING SOON

        .col-md-6
          .mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.demo-card-wide 
            .mdl-card__title.email
              h2.mdl-card__title-text UCLA Radio Department Manager Emails
            .mdl-card__supporting-text
              | Email our lovely managers.
            .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
              a.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect(target='_blank', href='#')
                | COMING SOON

      .row
        .col-md-6
          .mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.demo-card-wide 
            .mdl-card__title.faq
              h2.mdl-card__title-text DJ FAQs
            .mdl-card__supporting-text
              | Confused? Click the link.
            .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
              a.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect(target='_blank', href='#')
                | COMING SOON

